data.description: Assumable VA Mortgage Very Low interest rate. Why wait to build when you can seize this opportunity now?  This almost-new home is nestled in one of the most desirable gated communities and is ready for you to make it your own. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 baths, this centrally located gem in the SE area of Ocala is close to hospitals, doctors' offices, shopping, and schools. Situated on a lot that's over 1/3 of an acre, this home features a split bedroom plan, a stunning owner's suite with a tray ceiling, his and hers closets, and a wow-worthy owner's bath. The gourmet kitchen and Vaulted ceiling  add to the charm. Plus, the home is completely fenced, perfect for your furry friends. Home has already installed sprinkler system Water Softener and cameras. Don't miss out on the covered patio, ideal for enjoying the morning sunrise or relaxing with the Florida sunset. Ready to make that move? You're invited to tour this immaculately kept home that's eagerly awaiting a new owner!
